terminal_order_models.description: A high-end, touchscreen countertop solution. Includes power supply and paper roll in the box
Advanced, high performance pin pad with rich multimedia and commerce capabilities. Includes power supply and R232/Ethd Dongle 2m

Standalone mobile point of sale device with WiFi, Bluetooth, and 3G communication options, allowing secure payment acceptance anywhere without dependence on a smart device. The solution features a color touch screen capable of signature capture and is built on the Verifone Engage platform, enabling rich customer interaction at the point of sale
